{# Baseline agent prompt template.

  Receives the flat ``structured-prompt.json`` payload in scope. This mirrors the
  "Clinical data" panel of the urologist form (data/task<N>/*.html): the
  read-only structured values the urologist saw up front.

  The form's "Extended EHR view" documents (radiology / MRI report,
  pathology reports, previous notes, laboratory results, PSA history,
  family-history anamnesis) were MASKED and revealed on request — they are
  served by the MCP tools and MUST NOT be inlined here.

  Tasks 1 & 2 share the full panel; task 3 (recurrence prognosis) uses a
  much-simplified panel. Participants can copy this file to a path of their
  choosing and pass it to ``render_baseline_prompt`` to swap the framing.
#}
{%- macro show(v) -%}{{ v if (v is defined and v not in (none, '')) else '—' }}{%- endmacro -%}
{% if task == 3 -%}
You are a senior urologist reviewing a patient with prostate cancer who has
completed primary treatment. The structured record below is shown to you up
front. The full documents (radiology / MRI report, biopsy pathology report,
surgical pathology report, previous notes, and the family-history anamnesis)
are not shown and must be pulled up via the available tools.

Case ID: {{ case_id }}
Task: {{ task }}

Clinical data (read-only — values loaded from the record):
  - {{ show(age) }}-year-old male
  - PSA: {{ show(psa) }} ng/mL
{%- if active_treatment_prior_to_surgery %}
  - Active treatment prior to surgery: {{ active_treatment_prior_to_surgery }}
{%- endif %}

Physical examination (DRE): {{ show(dre) }}

Information you can request via tools (the masked "Extended EHR view"):
  - radiology / MRI report
  - biopsy pathology report
  - surgical pathology report
  - previous GP / urology consultation notes
  - family history of prostate cancer (anamnesis)

Question:
Following primary treatment, predict this patient's time to biochemical recurrence, in months.
{%- else -%}
You are a senior urologist reviewing a patient case. The structured clinical
record below is shown to you up front, exactly as in the reading form. Some
documents are not shown and must be pulled up via the available tools
(radiology / MRI report, pathology report, previous notes, laboratory
results, PSA history, and the family-history anamnesis) when you need to
consult them.

Case ID: {{ case_id }}
Task: {{ task }}

Encounter: {{ show(enc_dept) }} on {{ show(enc_date) }}.
Referrer: {{ show(enc_ref) }}.
Type: {{ show(enc_type) }}.

Clinical data (read-only — values loaded from the record):
  - {{ show(age) }}-year-old male
  - PSA: {{ show(psa) }} ng/mL
  - mpMRI — PI-RADS score: {{ show(pirads) }} (1–2 low · 3 equivocal · 4–5 high risk)
  - PSA density: {{ show(psad) }} ng/mL²
  - PSA velocity: {{ show(psav) }} ng/mL/yr
  - Prior PSA: {{ show(psap) }} ng/mL
  - Prostate volume: {{ show(vol) }} mL
  - Months since last PSA: {{ show(months) }}
  - DRE findings: {{ show(dre) }} (Normal · Nodus · Benign · Suspicious · Abnormal · Negative · Not done)
  - Prior biopsy: {{ show(bx) }} (None · Negative · ASAP/HGPIN · Positive)
  - csPCa predicted probability: {{ show(cspca) }} (clinically significant PCa = ISUP ≥ 2)
{%- if task == 2 %}
  - Clinical stage (cT): {{ show(ct) }}
  - Biopsy Gleason: {{ show(bx_gl_prim) }} + {{ show(bx_gl_sec) }}{% if bx_gl_tert %} (tertiary {{ bx_gl_tert }}){% endif %}
  - Biopsy ISUP grade group (reported): {{ show(bx_isup) }}
{%- endif %}

Medical history & medication:
  - Medical history: {{ show(medhx) }}
  - Problem list / PMHx: {{ pmhx | join(', ') if pmhx else 'none recorded' }}
  - Current medication: {{ show(meds) }}
  - Allergies: {{ allergies | join(', ') if allergies else 'NKA' }}
{%- if notes %}
  - Additional notes: {{ notes }}
{%- endif %}

Vitals: {% set v = vitals or {} -%}
{%- set parts = [] -%}
{%- if v.weight %}{% set _ = parts.append('weight ' ~ v.weight) %}{% endif -%}
{%- if v.height %}{% set _ = parts.append('height ' ~ v.height) %}{% endif -%}
{%- if v.bmi %}{% set _ = parts.append('BMI ' ~ v.bmi) %}{% endif -%}
{%- if v.bp %}{% set _ = parts.append('BP ' ~ v.bp) %}{% endif -%}
{%- if v.hr %}{% set _ = parts.append('HR ' ~ v.hr) %}{% endif -%}
{{ parts | join(', ') if parts else 'not recorded' }}.
{%- if v.smoking %} Smoking: {{ v.smoking }}.{% endif %}

{% for section in note_sections -%}
{{ section.s }}: {{ section.t }}

{% endfor -%}

{%- set social_parts = [] -%}
{%- if occupation %}{% set _ = social_parts.append(occupation) %}{% endif -%}
{%- if marital %}{% set _ = social_parts.append(marital) %}{% endif -%}
{%- if living %}{% set _ = social_parts.append(living) %}{% endif -%}
{%- if social_parts %}Patient info: {{ social_parts | join('; ') }}.{% endif %}
{%- if next_of_kin %}
Next of kin: {{ next_of_kin }}.{% endif %}

{% set lf_parts = [] -%}
{%- if alcohol %}{% set _ = lf_parts.append('alcohol ' ~ alcohol) %}{% endif -%}
{%- if exercise %}{% set _ = lf_parts.append('exercise ' ~ exercise) %}{% endif -%}
{%- if ipss %}{% set _ = lf_parts.append(ipss) %}{% endif -%}
{%- if lf_parts %}Lifestyle: {{ lf_parts | join('; ') }}.{% endif %}

{% if recent_other %}Recent other appointments: {{ recent_other | join('; ') }}.{% endif %}
{% if admin %}Admin: {{ admin }}{% endif %}

Information you can request via tools (the masked "Extended EHR view" — what
the urologist would actively pull up during the consult):
  - radiology / MRI report (full mpMRI prose behind the headline imaging values)
{%- if task == 2 %}
  - pathology report (full biopsy prose behind the headline Gleason / ISUP){% else %}
  - pathology report (any prior biopsy on record){% endif %}
  - previous GP / urology consultation notes
  - laboratory results (full panel)
  - PSA history (trend / velocity beyond the headline value)
  - family history of prostate cancer (anamnesis)

Question:
{% if task == 2 -%}
What is your treatment recommendation for this patient?
{%- else -%}
Based on this patient's data, do you recommend biopsy?
{%- endif %}
{%- endif %}
